RES osdtriplet
SUR SA
PIK RDY S3 S1
RDY S1 45
SUR SA
PIK THI S4 S2 2.0
THI S2 4
SUR SA
! Next line is a deliberate error (CUY is not a valid surface parameter):
PIK CUY S3 S1
! Save/reload round-trip: both pickups must survive and stay LIVE
! (targets track new source values after reload).  Note THI pickups were
! historically dropped from saves entirely -- this guards that fix.
SAV pickuptest
RES pickuptest
RDY S1 40
THI S2 5
SUR SA
! Removal: after PIKD the targets must stop tracking the source.
U L
PIKD RD,3
PIKD TH,4
EOS
RDY S1 60
THI S2 7
SUR SA
